OL,5, Former basketball star Magic Johnson   
OL,6, has been declared a billionaire by     
OL,7, Forbes, making him only the fourth     
OL,8, athlete to join the exclusive club.    
OL,10,FThe business magazine estimates        
OL,11,FJohnson's wealth at about $1.2bn       
OL,12,F(#990m).                               
OL,14,FThe other athlete billionaires are NBA 
OL,15,Fplayers Michael Jordan and Lebron      
OL,16,FJames, and the golfer Tiger Woods.     
OL,18,FJohnson has investments in numerous    
OL,19,Fcompanies including ownership stakes in
OL,20,Fvarious sports teams.                  
